Type Name Description
System.Uri url

The URL of the pull request.
System.Int32 id

The unique identifier of the pull request.
System.Int32 number

The number of the pull request within the repository.
System.String state

The state of the pull request, such as "open", "closed", or "merged".
System.Boolean locked

A value indicating whether the pull request is locked for comments or changes.
System.String title

The title of the pull request.
GitHubUser user

The user who created the pull request.
System.Collections.Generic.List<Label> labels

A list of labels assigned to the pull request.
System.DateTime updatedAt

The date and time when the pull request was last updated.
System.Nullable<System.DateTime> closedAt

The date and time when the pull request was closed, or null if it is not closed.
System.Nullable<System.DateTime> mergedAt

The date and time when the pull request was merged, or null if it is not merged.
